{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这里就是我们的圣城。\\n今天开始请多多关照，小蕾。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "彼此彼此，请多关照，\\n尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "众人在旅程中遇到了\\n拥有稀世计算能力的算术师——小蕾。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "因为有事相求，\\n尤蒂尔\\n便将小蕾带回了圣城。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "啊……我等你很久了！\\n小蕾！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "因为城内的财政状况很严峻，\\n所以想让专业人士帮忙看看……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "的确……这么大的建筑物，\\n再加上这么多人，\\n一定很不容易吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "伙食费自不必说，\\n蜡烛的费用应该也相当可观。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "没错！就是这样！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "真是太好了！\\n能帮我解决问题的人来城里了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊。\\n之前都是靠库菈乌一个人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以……小蕾，你能不能\\n给库菈乌的工作帮帮忙？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "嗯，乐意之至。算术师要的就是账簿！\\n账簿要的就是算术师！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "我会用自己的计算\\n让这座城的财政状况得到最大改善！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "真是太可靠了！\\n那就请你先看看这本账簿吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "交给我吧，小事一桩。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "那我就开始了！计算开始——\\n四万零五十三、八十二、三千零七十……\\n啪啪啪！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "好厉害……\\n一转眼就要算完了！\\n那个工具是？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "呵呵呵。这就是从东方太吾国\\n传来的计算工具——算盘！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶……叫“算盘”吗。好神奇，\\n仅仅是拨动小小的珠子\\n竟然就能完成计算。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "是啊，从没见过这种工具。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "对吧？这可是改变了\\n东方算术历史的一大发明。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "东方大国的文化传播到了\\n我出生的地方，比如这个算盘。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "好，算好了！\\n有几个错误，我已经改过来了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "噢……所有数据都整整齐齐！\\n账簿看起来都耀眼了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔……虽然我不是很懂，\\n但似乎是算得既细致又准确。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢谢你，小蕾。\\n真是帮大忙了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "不，现在道谢还太早。\\n我刚才只是改正了计算错误。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "账簿的重生……\\n现在才刚要开始！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "财务的铁则！节约10条！\\n第一条——“消耗品批量购买”！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "第二条——“重物要在当地购买”！\\n这样可以削减运费！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "原、原来如此……受教了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "还有很多呢！\\n第三条……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "就这样，遵照小蕾的节约10条，\\n圣城的财务状况得到了彻底的整改。\\n之后……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "呼，吃饱了吃饱了！\\n饭真好吃啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "而且今天的菜还多了一道，\\n让我身心都很满足。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "都是多亏小蕾。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "有她改善城里的财政状况，\\n资金才变得充裕了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "噢！那可太谢谢你了，\\n小蕾！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "呵呵，不客气。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "算术师吗……又多了一位好伙伴。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊，今后也要拜托你了，\\n小蕾！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110316_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小蕾",
            "context": "交给我吧！\\n我会用算术改变这座城的生活！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}